column5: i just see no point to keep trying.. life is not a good deal to me.. lazy or not.. i dont mind the label.. nothing matters to me..
it seems like life hates me.. pulling a joke thats not funny anymore.. i dont know what to do... i just want to escape this hell hole.. :/
it doesnt matter, post anywhere you like :)

no, you are stronger than you think,,
those people hate themselves, not you personally, they just used you to feel better about themselves..
be strong and confident and happy, they will exhaust themselves..

hey you can talk to me...
when human died, like any other living being, we simply back home to non existence...
nothing to fear, fear only exist in the mind.. its a concept..

i feel the same, for fact, i did something that normally works out 99% of the time, but the universe said "not today" ....
haahahahahaha, i just can't understand .....
woke up with "girei" playing in my head :|
maybe the virus said you dont deserved to die yet, here suffer some more.. happening to me.. the fever is gone.. :(
try to count the "yes", maybe it could help.. maybe not.. i get a striking "no" too through decades.. so i know your pain..
why i didnt die yet, you disappointed me, covid,, this is your only chance..

it is pointless, true..
but on a flip side, we are free to make any point we want..
life is only a blip, do whatever we want..
fvck depression, it means nothing anymore to me..
im leaving it..
thanks for the virtual hug
i just hate ignorant people, just how high they are in their high castle.. ignorance and stupidity know no bounds..
yeah me too.. i love the night more than anything
thats exactly how i feel, they just dont care, they only care about themselves, everything relate to them is the most important, i hate people

tbh i cant relate my depression to Joaquin's joker character, its too weak for me.. though i can relate to his other movie called: "you were never really here"
it was more accurate depiction personally..
my dream changed a bit, instead of getting shot in the head, now my head getting crushed to the concrete, i guess it is an improvement,,
you can do it
it will be alright, i hope..
i can totally relate to the first paragraph, i cant even finish anything
i want to get better, but when i tried stepping in that direction, anxiety triggered and stopped me, then im back to dark cycle again, how do i get out of this shithole idk,, f,,
i hope 2019 is my worst year ever, please lie to me, say everything getting brighter, that all the pain will go away.. please 2020 save me.. please
your dad always love you and wanted the best for your life, you can cherish the memories and honour his legacy by living your best, stay strong mate, make him proud..
just chat here if you want
im here if you want to talk
say you will listen to her and be there for her, every single day, dont tell her to do anything she doesn't want to, just listen.. if she's ready to talk.. she will..
same
im here too if you need extra friend

I'm in the same spot as you, i know how to be normal, but i don't want to, that's the problem, 
this mental block is killing me inside
i can't cry either, but when i saw a simple act of kindness from random people, i cried a river, good to know humanity still thrives somewhere
i virtually accept you :)
please call your family, we all need each other.. please stay alive..
comparison is not healthy, stay true to yourself, we can only solve the problem if we recognize that we have one, dont suppress it..

take your meds with you, let closest coworkers know about your condition, so they can help if needed, 
tell yourself everything is alright, nothing in the world can hurt you, being panicked is okay too, you can calm yourself, you are in control.. best wishes
what is the most painful thought you have? let out your source of depression.. it can help a bit.. we will listen to you..
well, you must be good at something, you can focus on your strength if you want.. dont give up

tough life, but you made a lot of progress, go for therapy if you want, it will definitely help, you are doing very good so far considering all the bad stuff that happened.. wish you the best for next year.. peace

past few days means it was just a bad event or circumstances? 
give it some time, maybe things get okay again, wish you well..
this is the only corner of the internet that comforts me, have a good night me, you need it
me too :(
good for you mate :)
everytime i feel im at the lowest, life always surprise me by defining what a low really looks like..
at least your sense of humor is good, and you are a humble person
ugly hearted people exist, i know
another low blow by life, i just want an ending, a happy one if possible, is it too much to ask for?
what is ugly? such a thing is not exist and very subjective, be confident to be who you are, you are good enough to be loved, you will find people who care and love you, peace
robot lives matter, being robot is okay, do not shutdown yet, from your robot friend..
impossible.. i am immune to motivation..
you are heard
i want to live fully, this is a lie i say to myself everyday now, for let it come true,,
i like your spirit, i wish i can be strong as you, best wishes for your 2020
hello to all, i love you all
because we experienced more pain than most people?
i just want a hole in my head, plain simple
when i am in down cycle, i become the most quiet one, just losing interest of everything, so i dont hang around people anymore like i used to, they bored me now

you can open up little by little, talk to your friend or coworker about small stuff you are afraid of, ask their opinion about things you worried about, keep it light, you may find some people that may care and share your feeling, dont be scared, we are all alone in this world, but you will find friends that are genuinely care, best wishes
its a dilemma indeed, i dont want my parent to suffer, i keep being alive for them, i hope i can be cured for them
hey dont say like that, theres still friendly people out there that look past the surface, i dont mind chatting to stranger regardless of their look

dont worry and compare yourself to other people, just do it on your pace, you will succeed, believe in yourself, either engineering or other course, as long as you really want it, you can make it, good luck..

now you make me remember my past, my dad used to say the same, that i should hang myself because im useless and not up to his expectations, that hurts a lot, what a violent past back then, but now i know he didnt mean it, hes just frustated with himself and throw his anger and self hatred to me,, but i hope you can resolve the problem with your father.. over time..
how can i help? you can talk here, i will listen and provide feedback if i can..
hey you can talk here, bad things happen in this world, but good people still exist, dont lose hope :|
lol that must be annoying :)
out of nowhere, my brain keep playing tristesse as background song, damn it brain,,
im sorry i cant help, i wish i can do something, stay strong and good wishes to you and your family, hopefully peace will win soon
just another weird dream, climbing a very high building, almost die in the process,  but after i reached the top, the door is locked, cant go anywhere but down again, very frustrating
being fat and poor is no crime, fvck value system, just do what we need to do, fvck the rest.. :)
dont drown yet, keep a fight for another day..
if someone said that to me, god knows what will happen to their nose.. then see if they can work it out..
diagnosed? but i dont have money for you, professionals, to validate my depression nor i need to.. but then again who cares.. really.. lol

if you are sad then feel sad, if you want to cry, then cry as hard as you need, no point to control and hold anything inside, suppressed feeling is not good, but drowning too long in sadness is not good too, i guess....
i dont know why i cant cry anymore maybe it made no sense anymore, everything hurts yet pointless at the same time... no happy feeling nor sad feeling, just a joke of the universe, which is me.. :|
its ok to be like that, dont need to feel sorry.. thats life.. i feel alone too in this whole chaotic busy world..
caffeine is life, nothing makes sense without it, i got heavy headache when i skip coffee
try different food, of course it has no purpose, but exploring good food can be fun too

right to be depressed? lol
just leave the therapist, he wont get it if he said something like that

why you feel you dont deserve it? 
its ok to cry.. i hate myself a lot too but i cant cry anymore.. lol
your body cells fighting to keep you alive, thats how you didnt die.. maybe.. but i hope you're getting better..
thats very convenient situation lol
i dont think death is matter anymore, more so to life, i am at peace now, embracing the joke of the universe
how to get amnesia? i want to forget me
every time i wake up i point my hand into my mouth, and trigger it like it is something else
how to do things you need to do? i just cant force myself to do it.. i wish i can brainwash myself to be ignorant superficial people for once.. so i can do things like "normal" people do..
true
not working for me, tried living on the road, going to new places for 4 months, some good experiences some bad experiences, so i come back home, depressed again but at least i could sleep well
